sentences.english: Now, there are some immediate bad explanations for this.

sentences.english: Now I am making an attempt to explain the positions of categories such as primitive accumulation and some others.

sentences.english: In this paper, we propose a mathematical model of planar reflector on the Solar pond.
sentences.chinese: 本文提出了太陽池反射板的數學模型，並進行了計算。

sentences.english: With the chance of Universiade, Shenzhen proposes to build a voluntary city with the effort of all citizens.
sentences.chinese: 借大運會契機，深圳提出全民共建“志願之城”。

sentences.english: The government brought two hundred eighty-five charges against him, mostly for murder.
sentences.chinese: 政府對他提出二百八十五費，主要用於謀殺。

sentences.english: But recently some people presented a new algebraic diagonalization method.

sentences.english: At no time, though, did Reagan ever criticize the United Nations specifically.
sentences.chinese: 但里根從未對聯合國提出過明確的批評。

sentences.english: A new type of continuous contact model was developed for a spatial revolute joint.

sentences.english: A simple hierarchical coarse-to-fine edge detection method based on the direction of potential edge elements is given.

sentences.english: A new type of two-branch diversity reception system is presented.

sentences.english: Finally, some advice was put forward on the research directions of FOD tolerance design technology in China.

sentences.english: An automatic software-development technique of interactive interface for intelligent instruments is presented in this paper.

sentences.english: His suggestion that Jiulong city must be a commercial port was strategic insight.
sentences.chinese: 提出了闢九龍爲商埠等有戰略眼光的建議。
